{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"你当赞颂你至高主的大名超绝万物，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"他创造万物并使各物匀称。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他预定万物，而加以引导。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"他生出牧草，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"然后使它变成黑色的枯草。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"我将使你诵读，故你不会忘记，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"除非安拉所欲忘记的。他的确知道显著的和隐微的言行。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"我将使你遵循平易的道路，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"故你当教诲众人，如果教诲有裨于他们的话。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"畏主的人，将觉悟；"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"薄命的人，将退避，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"他将入于大火，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"然后，在火里不死也不活。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"纯洁者必定成功，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"他记念他的主的尊名，而谨守拜功。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"不然，你们却选择今世的生活；"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"其实，后世是更好的，是更长久的。"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"这确是载在古经典中的，"},{"SurahNumber":87,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"载在易卜拉欣和穆萨的经典中的。"}]}